    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily commuting or a first car. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are in working order, though you may notice typical signs of high mileage such as minor fluid seeps and a less-than-perfect idle. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, small dents, and some paint fading on the roof and hood. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and a few stains, but all essential electronics and climate controls remain functional. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
      "price": 18500.0,
