    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, reflecting meticulous care and an absolute refusal to compromise on maintenance. For the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection, this unit offers an investment-grade acquisition opportunity. Every surface and mechanical component adheres to the most rigorous standards of excellence, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut.",
      "price": 48500.0,
