      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely thrilled to be listing this beauty! It\u2019s in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, so you won\u2019t find a single scratch or speck of dust anywhere. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You\u2019ve gotta see it in person to believe how pristine it is! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
