    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Presenting a definitive E92 M3 in collector-grade condition. At its heart lies the S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, a high-revving unit featuring individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio. This example features the sought-after 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock. Preventative maintenance is comprehensive, including treated rod bearings and reinforced throttle actuators. The suspension geometry remains factory-spec, utilizing the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) system for adaptable damping rates. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and a flawless cabin, this vehicle satisfies the most discerning mechanical inspection.",
